description:
This is a 17 minute workout called '3 Day Calisthenics Workout Plan | FULL PROGRAM' from the channel Summerfunfitness.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
